               <p>London Cases, First Jury. Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>891. 
               
                  <persName id="t18240603-75-defend665" type="defendantName">
                     JOSEPH 
                     JOHNSON
                  <interp inst="t18240603-75-defend665" type="surname" value="JOHNSON"></interp>
